Know these feelings guy, I play squishy mages very much (like Veigar but mostly Azir) and I really, really have problems vs Yasuo because he just dashes through my minions, takes my half life away with one q and dashes back, doing this 3 times and I am dead, even with heal pots. That Champion is just like: No, you don't zone me and you don't trade with me, I'm just the god of mid lane ... . Just looking at streams of TSM Bjergsen, I also thought: Lol, even Bjegsen has no concept against Yasuo ... . So just someone tell me again that this champion is not overpowered ... I hate him so, so much like no other champions because even if you win early game to him like I normally do as Kindred, you won't be able to fight him in mid or late game because he just has a late game build with 3k gold. RIOT PLS why don't you accept that Yasuo is defenetly too strong? Or is it just like Lee Sin who doesn't get a nerf because too many people would be completely pissed off that they can't play their cool overpowered Champion?

See you soon in the Rift, I hope Yasuo finally gets nerfed, like taking his Crit passive into his Ult, scaling with his Ults level or something like this. This would make him much more balanced ...
