Oh I'm not saying start boots, I'm saying try and drive him out of lane pre-6 and get boots first back so when he's post 6 he has a harder time landing a tornado. I start Doran's 9/10 and then first back I try and have enough for Idol, and boots to allow me to harass more and dodge more of his. Plus the crit mastery isn't worth as much until he gets his crit core finished which if your good at Azir you should be able to delay until you get Nashor's online and some of Morello 
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}} 

When he gets Shiv he gets scarier but u can delay it fairly well if u can zone him off CS, but I agree Yasuo is too popular this patch. They should nerf the mastery so it only functions off of basic attack crits and not basic attack like abilities (Yasuo Q, Yi Q, etc...), and either up the CD or reduce/remove the cooldown while nerfing the heal. I think healing 3% of critical hit damage on no CD wouldn't be AS bad don't you?
